<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Routine Name="seqRobot_Stack" Type="RLL">
  <Description><![CDATA[step 200 = stack]]></Description>
  <RLLContent>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 200:
Beginning of Stack Component
Decide what type of part is in process, then apply offsets to tool (if vision is applied, or not)
This tool is for the upper touch position
]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,200)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[15],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actStackPressure.ACT.Extend_Req) ,[XIC(Bit_Processing_Discrete) [MOV(Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Discrete_X_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.X) ,MOV(Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Discrete_Y_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Y) ,MOV(Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Discrete_R_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Roll) ,MOV(0,s800_Loc0_Offset.Z) ] ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Cathode) [ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.X,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Cathode_X_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.X) ,ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.Y,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Cathode_Y_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Y) ,ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.Roll,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Cathode_R_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Roll) ,MOV(1.85,s800_Loc0_Offset.Z) ] ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Anode) [ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.X,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Anode_X_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.X) ,ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.Y,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Anode_Y_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Y) ,ADD(s800_Vision_Offset.Roll,Machine_Run_Recipe.R_Anode_R_Offset.Value,s800_Loc0_Offset.Roll) ,NEQ(intLayer_Anode_Type,2) MOV(0.56,s800_Loc0_Offset.Z) ,EQU(intLayer_Anode_Type,2) MOV(1.09,s800_Loc0_Offset.Z) ] ] ,[COP(s800.LocationConfig[Loc_Stack],s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp],1) ,ADD(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.X,s800_Loc0_Offset.X,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.X) ,ADD(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Y,s800_Loc0_Offset.Y,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Y) ,MOV(380,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z) ,ADD(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Roll,s800_Loc0_Offset.Roll,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Roll) ,MOV(205,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 205:
Move to Stack Location approach, WITH OFFSETS FROM PREVIOUS STEP]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,205)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[16],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ]XIC(I_Stack_Pressure_OK)[ONS(Machine_Oneshots[4].11) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Jump_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Jump_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Jump_Complete) [MOV(210,seqRobot.Step) ,MOV(0,s800.Commands.Approach_Height) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 210:
Move down to Mylar]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,210)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[17],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[2].7) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,COP(s800.LocationConfig[Loc_Stack].Coordinate.Z,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z,1) ,MUL(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed,0.75,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,ADD(s800_Loc0_Offset.Z,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [MOV(215,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 215
At stack location touch, open the wings]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,215)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[18],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actStackWings.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Fault) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Extend_Complete) [MOV(220,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 220:
Turn on Stack Vacuum, apply offset to lower stack
changed b on GRT from 1 to 0 so wings close on first layer (this is to unroll edges of discrete placed on top of first layer) - jca 3-14-13
changed code so it always closes the wings (which not included the first part for second stacked battery) - jca 6-6-14]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,220)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[19],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIC(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Complete) [COP(Machine_Run_Recipe.Stack_Z_Handoff_Height.Value,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z,1) ,[MOV(225,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 225:
Travel past wings]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,225)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[20],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[4].12) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [MOV(230,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 230:
Ckose stack wings]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,230)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[21],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actStackWings.ACT.Retract_Req) ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Fault) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Retract_Complete) [MOV(235,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 235:
Release EOAT vacuum
Check if last layer]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,235)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[22],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Retract_Req) ,XIC(actRobotVac.ACT.Retract_Complete) [[[NEQ(StackData.Current_Stack_Layer,Machine_Run_Recipe.Number_of_Layers.Value) ,XIC(Bit_Working_On_Queue_Battery) ] MOV(240,seqRobot.Step) ,NEQ(seqRobot.Step,240) MOV(253,seqRobot.Step) ] ,OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Abort) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 240:
Depart at slow speed so stack platform keeps up
]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,240)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[23],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[8].18) [MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(15,s800.Commands.Approach_Height) ,MOV(25,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,MOV(25,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Acceleration) ,MOV(25,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Deceleration) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [MOV(245,seqRobot.Step) ,MOV(0,s800.Commands.Approach_Height) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 245:
Travel to up, stack was not done]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,245)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[24],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[4].13) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(100,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,MOV(100,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Deceleration) ,MOV(100,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Acceleration) ,MOV(393.9,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Jump_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,GRT(s800.Robot.Percent_Move_Complete,Real_Check_During_Move) XIO(Bit_Working_On_Queue_Battery) OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Jump_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Jump_Complete) [MOV(250,seqRobot.Step) ,MOV(0,s800.Commands.Approach_Height) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 250:
Add a layer to the stack and go back to the decision step
copy in trace data if vacuum check is ok
check stack vacuum on first layer only]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,250)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[25],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][XIO(Bit_Working_On_Queue_Battery) [OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,OTL(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIC(actRobotVac.ACT.Extend_Complete) XIC(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Complete) [XIO(I_EOAT_Vac) [XIC(I_Stack_Vac) ,GRT(StackData.Current_Stack_Layer,1) ] [XIC(Bit_Processing_Cathode) [CPS(StackData.Cathode_Data_from_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Discrete) CPS(Discrete_Just_Picked,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Anode) [CPS(StackData.Anode_Data_from_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,AFI() JSR(subRFIDtoPIA,1,0) ,[OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Abort) ,ADD(1,StackData.Current_Stack_Layer,StackData.Current_Stack_Layer) ,MOV(260,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ,[XIC(I_EOAT_Vac) OTL(Bit_Robot_Part_Stuck_Trigger) ,LEQ(StackData.Current_Stack_Layer,1) XIO(I_Stack_Vac) OTL(Bit_Stack_Part_Missing_Trigger) ] [MOV(200,seqRobot.Step) ,OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ] ,XIC(Bit_Working_On_Queue_Battery) MOV(252,seqRobot.Step) ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 252: Working on Queue battery 
move in trace data

JEO - Deleted StackDataQueue[].Layer_String MOV commands from this rung since I added them to rtTrayTracker, this is were it is done for the normal stack data.
Added layer data transfer for the two additional layers that we are allowing for a queued stack.  - 05/14/15 ]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,252)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[26],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,OTL(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIC(actRobotVac.ACT.Extend_Complete) XIC(actStackFixtureVac.ACT.Extend_Complete) [XIO(I_EOAT_Vac) [XIC(I_Stack_Vac) ,GRT(intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer,1) ] [MOV(20,seqRobot.Step) ,[XIC(Bit_Processing_Cathode) [CPS(StackData.Cathode_Data_from_RFID,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Discrete) CPS(Discrete_Just_Picked,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Anode) [CPS(StackData.Anode_Data_from_RFID,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,MOV(2,StackDataQueue[intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer].Layer_Status) ,ADD(intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer,1,intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer) ] ,OTL(actRobotVac.ACT.Abort) ] ,[XIC(I_EOAT_Vac) OTL(Bit_Robot_Part_Stuck_Trigger) ,EQU(intCurrent_Queued_Stack_Layer,1) XIO(I_Stack_Vac) OTL(Bit_Stack_Part_Missing_Trigger) ] [MOV(200,seqRobot.Step) ,OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[TOP ANODE: move to stack touch, then move to stack transfer, then open wings

Go to nominal stack location without offsets, that way robot aligns to transfer gripper

JEO - Only move in z-axis. - 05/15/15]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,253)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[27],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[2].1) [MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,ADD(s800.World_Current_Value.Z,10,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z) ,MOV(s800.World_Current_Value.X,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.X) ,MOV(s800.World_Current_Value.Y,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Y) ,MUL(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed,0.1,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [MOV(254,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[GoTo Stack location with Z-Offset

JEO - Added. - 05/15/15]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,254)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[28],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[2].12) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,COP(s800.LocationConfig[Loc_Stack],s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp],1) ,MOV(s800.World_Current_Value.Z,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z) ,MUL(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed,0.1,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) NEQ(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [COP(Machine_Run_Recipe.Stack_Z_Handoff_Height.Value,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z,1) ,[MOV(257,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[TOP ANODE: move to stack touch, then move to stack transfer, then open wings

JEO - Changed step number to 257. 05/15/15]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,257)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[29],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][ONS(Machine_Oneshots[6].8) [MOV(s800.Robot.MotionCounter,intMotionCounter) ,MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) ,COP(s800.LocationConfig[Loc_Stack],s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp],1) ,COP(Machine_Run_Recipe.Stack_Z_Handoff_Height.Value,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Coordinate.Z,1) ,MUL(s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed,0.1,s800.LocationConfig[iLocTemp].Speed) ,OTL(s800.Commands.Move_Req) ] ,XIC(s800.Robot.statFaulted) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ,XIO(s800.Commands.Move_Req) MOV(iLocTemp,s800.Commands.MoveLocationIndex) XIC(s800.Robot.Move_Complete) [MOV(259,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 259:
Last Layer, copy data and return, currently holding down on stack

JEO - Changed step number to 259. 05/15/15]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,259)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)[XIC(System.Auto) XIO(Bit_RobotOnlyStepMode) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][[OTL(actStackWings.ACT.Extend_Req) ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Fault) OTL(seqRobot.Fault) ] ,XIC(actStackWings.ACT.Extend_Complete) [XIC(Bit_Processing_Cathode) [CPS(StackData.Cathode_Data_from_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Discrete) CPS(Discrete_Just_Picked,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ,XIC(Bit_Processing_Anode) [CPS(StackData.Anode_Data_from_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].RFID_Data,1) ,CPS(String_RFID,StackData.Layer[StackData.Current_Stack_Layer].Placed_Layer_Trace_Data,1) ] ,JSR(subRFIDtoPIA,1,0) ,ADD(1,StackData.Current_Stack_Layer,StackData.Current_Stack_Layer) ,[MOV(9,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ] ] ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
    <Rung Type="N">
      <Comment><![CDATA[Step 260: Home Robot

JEO - Bypassing this move to home step since it isn't needed.  Robot won't crash with this step removed.  With this removed cycle time is greatly improved. 11/10/14]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[EQU(seqRobot.Step,260)XIC(seqRobot.Perm)CONCAT(Message_Robot[30],K_Str_Blank,seqRobot.Status)[XIC(System.Auto) ,XIC(seqRobot.StepNext) ][MOV(9,seqRobot.Step) ,OTU(seqRobot.StepNext) ];]]></Text>
    </Rung>
  </RLLContent>
</Routine>